[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 3.12.1"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 3.12.1 are now fixed in Tails 3.13.

We **strongly** encourage you to
[[upgrade to Tails 3.13|news/version_3.13]] as soon as possible.

